      <title>必和必拓以 30 亿美元收购 Filo 南美铜矿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/bhp-group-and-canada-s-lundin-mining-buy-copper-miner-filo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团有限公司 (BHP Group Ltd.) 刚刚遭到英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 的拒绝，就突然收购了 Filo Corp，并与 Lundin Mining Corp. 联手以 30 亿美元的价格获得了南美铜资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/bhp-group-and-canada-s-lundin-mining-buy-copper-miner-filo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 00:02:38 GMT</pubDate>
